name: Klink
introduction: The two minigears that mesh together are predetermined. Each will rebound from other minigears without meshing.
introduction_tw: 2個身體的組合是定好了的。和別的身體不會咬合會分離。
introduction_en: The two minigears that mesh together are predetermined. Each will rebound from other minigears without meshing.
introduction_vn: Sự kết hợp của 2 cơ thể được thiết lập. Sẽ tách rời mà không kìm chặt với cơ thể khác
introduction_kr: 2개의 몸은 쌍둥이보다도 가깝다. 다른 몸과 있으면 제대로 맞물리지 못한다.
location: Buff Support: Rage recovery for back line
location_en: Buff Support: Rage recovery for back line
location_vn: Phụ Trợ Tăng Lợi: hồi phục Nộ Khí hàng sau
location_kr: 스탯 강화 서포트: 후방 라인 분노 회복

name: Klang
introduction: By changing the direction in which it rotates, it communicates its feelings to others. When angry, it rotates faster.
introduction_tw: 通過改變旋轉方向與同伴傳達情感。越憤怒旋轉速度越快。
introduction_en: By changing the direction in which it rotates, it communicates its feelings to others. When angry, it rotates faster.
introduction_vn: Bày tỏ tình cảm với đồng đội bằng cách xoay chuyển phương hướng. Càng giận dữ tốc độ xoay càng nhanh.
introduction_kr: 회전 방향을 바꿔서 동료에게 감정을 전한다. 화가 나면 회전이 빨라진다.
location: Buff Support: Rage recovery for back line
location_en: Buff Support: Rage recovery for back line
location_vn: Phụ Trợ Tăng Lợi: hồi phục Nộ Khí hàng sau
location_kr: 스탯 강화 서포트: 후방 라인 분노 회복

name: Klinklang
introduction: Its red core functions as an energy tank. It fires the charged energy through its spikes into an area.
introduction_tw: 紅色核心擔當著能量罐的角色。填充好的能量會從尖刺射向周圍。
introduction_en: Its red core functions as an energy tank. It fires the charged energy through its spikes into an area.
introduction_vn: Lõi đỏ hoạt động như một bể năng lượng. Năng lượng đầy sẽ bắn gai nhọn ra xung quanh.
introduction_kr: "붉은 코어는 에너지 탱크의 역할을 하며, 충전된 에너지는 가시를 통해 주변에 발사한다."
location: Buff Support: Rage recovery for back line
location_en: Buff Support: Rage recovery for back line
location_vn: Phụ Trợ Tăng Lợi: hồi phục Nộ Khí hàng sau
location_kr: 스탯 강화 서포트: 후방 라인 분노 회복

name: Litwick
introduction: Litwick, Candle Pokémon. Appears in dark places and can illuminate the surroundings to help... people... guide... the... way...
introduction_tw: 燭光靈，蠟燭寶可夢。會出現在漆黑的地方，點上燈火，照亮周圍，並且主……動……為……人……帶……路……
introduction_en: Litwick, Candle Pokémon. Appears in dark places and can illuminate the surroundings to help... people... guide... the... way...
introduction_kr: "불켜미, 양초 포켓몬, 어두운 곳에 나타나 등불을 켜 주변을 밝힌다. 사람들에게 길을 안내해 준다..."

name: Lampent
introduction: Lampent, Lamp Pokémon. Lampents float through the air to move. They used to live in deep forests, but now they can be found living in cities as well.
introduction_tw: 燈火幽靈，油燈寶可夢。飄浮在空中來進行移動。過去雖然都居住于森林深處，不過現在也開始移居到大城市中
introduction_en: Lampent, Lamp Pokémon. Lampents float through the air to move. They used to live in deep forests, but now they can be found living in cities as well.
introduction_kr: "램프라, 램프 포켓몬, 공중에 뜬 채로 움직인다. 과거에는 숲 깊은 곳에 주로 서식했지만, 지금은 대도시로 이주하기 시작했다."

name: Chandelure
introduction: It is said that in houses that use Chandelure as a lighting device, death comes one after another.
introduction_tw: 據說在用水晶燈火靈來充當照明設備的房子裡，喪事會接連不斷。
introduction_en: It is said that in houses that use Chandelure as a lighting device, death comes one after another.
introduction_kr: 샹델라를 등불 대용으로 사용했던 저택에서는 장례식이 끊이지 않았다고 한다.

name: Axew
introduction: Axew marks its territory by making scratch marks on trees with its tusks, which regrow if they fall out.
introduction_tw: 用牙齒在樹木上留下傷痕，作為領地的標記。牙齒即使折斷也會馬上長出來。
introduction_en: Axew marks its territory by making scratch marks on trees with its tusks, which regrow if they fall out.
introduction_vn: Dùng răng để lại dấu vết trên cây, để làm ký hiệu lãnh địa. Dù răng bị gãy cũng sẽ mọc ra ngay lập tức.
introduction_kr: 송곳니로 나무에 상처를 내어 영역 표시를 한다. 송곳니는 부서지더라도 곧바로 자라난다.

name: Fraxure
introduction: A broken tusk will not grow back, so it diligently sharpens its tusks on river rocks after the end of a battle.
introduction_tw: 牙齒不會再次生長，因此戰鬥結束後就會使用河灘的岩石仔細地磨牙。
introduction_en: A broken tusk will not grow back, so it diligently sharpens its tusks on river rocks after the end of a battle.
introduction_vn: Răng sẽ không mọc lại, vì vậy sau khi trận đấu kết thúc dùng tảng đá trên bãi biển để mài răng.
introduction_kr: "부러진 어금니는 다시 자라나지 않기 때문에, 싸움이 끝나면 강가의 바위에 어금니를 열심히 간다."

name: Haxorus
introduction: Their sturdy tusks will stay sharp even if used to cut steel beams. These Pokémon are covered in hard armor.
introduction_tw: 有著即使切斬工字鋼也不會傷刃的堅固牙齒。全身被堅硬的鎧甲覆蓋著。
introduction_en: Their sturdy tusks will stay sharp even if used to cut steel beams. These Pokémon are covered in hard armor.
introduction_vn: Hàm răng chắc khỏe dù cắt thép cũng không bị tổn thương. Toàn bộ được bao phủ bởi áo giáp cứng chắc.
introduction_kr: 철골을 잘라도 이가 나가지 않는 강인한 송곳니를 지녔다. 전신이 단단한 갑주로 덮여 있다.

name: Cubchoo
introduction: Their snot is a barometer of health. When healthy, their snot is sticky and the power of their ice moves increases.
introduction_tw: 鼻涕是健康的晴雨錶。身體狀況好，粘性就變強，冰的招式威力也會增強。
introduction_en: Their snot is a barometer of health. When healthy, their snot is sticky and the power of their ice moves increases.
introduction_vn: Nước mũi là phong vũ biểu khỏe mạnh. Sức khỏe tốt, độ dính mạnh hơn, sức mạnh chiêu thức băng cũng sẽ tăng lên
introduction_kr: 콧물은 건강의 척도다. 상태가 좋으면 점성이 높아지고 얼음 기술의 위력도 증가한다.
location_kr: 얼음 타입 공격: 스피드 피해 증가

name: Beartic
introduction: It freezes its breath to create fangs and claws of ice to fight with. Cold northern areas are its habitat.
introduction_tw: 讓吐出的氣息凍結，製造冰牙和冰爪進行戰鬥。生活在北方的寒冷土地上。
introduction_en: It freezes its breath to create fangs and claws of ice to fight with. Cold northern areas are its habitat.
introduction_vn: Đóng băng hơi thở, tạo răng băng và móng băng để tiến hành chiến đấu. Sống ở vùng đất phía bắc lạnh lẽo
introduction_kr: 내뱉은 숨을 얼려버려 얼음 이빨이나 손톱을 만들어 싸운다. 북쪽의 한랭 지대에서 생활한다.
location_kr: 얼음 타입 공격: 스피드 피해 증가

name: Cryogonal
introduction: They are composed of ice crystals. They capture prey with chains of ice, freezing the prey at -148° F.
introduction_tw: 使用冰的結晶所形成的鎖綁住獵物，使其凍結到零下100度。
introduction_en: They are composed of ice crystals. They capture prey with chains of ice, freezing the prey at -148° F.
introduction_vn: Dùng khóa được hình thành từ kết tinh băng để trói con mồi, khiến nó đóng băng đến âm 100 độ.
introduction_kr: "얼음 결정으로 만들어진 사슬로 먹이를 휘감아 잡고, 영하 100도로 얼려버린다."
location: Ice-type front line hero: Freezes all targets
location_en: Ice-type front line hero: Freezes all targets
location_kr: 얼음 타입 전방 라인: 전체 얼음

name: Deino
introduction: Lacking sight, it's unaware of its surroundings, so it bumps into things and eats anything that moves.
introduction_tw: 因為不瞭解周圍的情形，所以會不斷地到處亂撞，撞到活物時就咬住吃。
introduction_en: Lacking sight, it's unaware of its surroundings, so it bumps into things and eats anything that moves.
introduction_vn: Do không hiểu rõ tình hình, nên không ngừng va chạm xung quanh, chạm trúng vật sống sẽ cắn để ăn
introduction_kr: "주변의 모습을 모르기 때문에, 닥치는 대로 부딪쳐서는 움직이는 것을 물어 먹어치운다."
location: Multiple damage hits: Stealing both attack stats
location_en: Multiple damage hits: Stealing both attack stats
location_vn: Sát Thương Nhiều Lần: đánh cắp song công

name: Zweilous
introduction: After it has eaten up all the food in its territory, it moves to another area. Its two heads do not get along.
introduction_tw: 如果吃光了領地內的食物，就會向其他土地移動。2個頭之間關係惡劣。
introduction_en: After it has eaten up all the food in its territory, it moves to another area. Its two heads do not get along.
introduction_vn: Nếu ăn hết thức ăn trong lãnh địa, sẽ di chuyển đến vùng đất khác. Mối quan hệ giữa hai bên rất tệ.
introduction_kr: 영역 안의 먹이를 다 먹으면 다른 곳의 지역으로 이동한다. 2개의 머리는 서로 사이가 나쁘다.
location: Multiple damage hits: Stealing both attack stats
location_en: Multiple damage hits: Stealing both attack stats
location_vn: Sát Thương Nhiều Lần: đánh cắp song công

name: Hydreigon
introduction: It responds to movement by attacking. This scary, three-headed Pokémon devours everything in its path.
introduction_tw: 對活動物體發生反應並展開襲擊，用3個頭吃光一切的恐怖寶可夢。
introduction_en: It responds to movement by attacking. This scary, three-headed Pokémon devours everything in its path.
introduction_vn: Horror Pokémo phản ứng với vật thể sống và tiến hành tấn công, dùng 3 cái đầu có thể ăn hết mọi thứ
introduction_kr: "움직이는 것에 반응해 덮치고, 3개의 머리로 먹어치우는 무시무시한 포켓몬."
location: Multiple damage hits: Stealing both attack stats
location_en: Multiple damage hits: Stealing both attack stats
location_vn: Sát Thương Nhiều Lần: đánh cắp song công

name: Larvesta
introduction: Larvesta, Torch Pokémon. Can be found at the base of volcanoes. They are able to shoot fire from their five horns in order to repel enemies.
introduction_tw: 燃燒蟲，火炬寶可夢。棲息在火山的山腳下。會從五隻角中發出火焰，將前來襲擊的敵人擊退。
introduction_en: Larvesta, Torch Pokémon. Can be found at the base of volcanoes. They are able to shoot fire from their five horns in order to repel enemies.
introduction_kr: 활화르바, 횃불 포켓몬.화산의 산기슭에 서식한다.다섯 모서리에서 화염을 내며 날아오는 적을 격퇴한다.

name: Volcarona
introduction: Volcarona, Sun Pokémon, evolved form of Larvesta. When the sky is dark from volcanic ash, Volcarona are born from a cocoon of burning flames and their flame has the power to replace the sun. In ancient murals, Volcarona are depicted as the god of fire.
introduction_tw: 火神蛾，太陽寶可夢，燃燒蟲進化型。從熊熊燃燒的火焰之繭中誕生，因為火山灰而使得地面壹片黑暗時，火神蛾的火焰可以代替太陽，在古代的壁畫上被描繪為火之神。
introduction_en: Volcarona, Sun Pokémon, evolved form of Larvesta. When the sky is dark from volcanic ash, Volcarona are born from a cocoon of burning flames and their flame has the power to replace the sun. In ancient murals, Volcarona are depicted as the god of fire.
introduction_kr: 불카모스，태양 포켓몬.활화르바 진화형. 활활 타오르는 화염의 굳은살에서 태어나 화산재로 인해 지면이 어두울 때 불카모스의 화염이 태양을 대신하여 고대 벽화에서 불의 신으로 묘사된다.

name: Cobalion
introduction_tw: 聖劍士的領導者，擁有鋼鐵的身體和心靈，為了守護寶可夢與人類爭鬥的傳說的寶可夢

name: Terrakion
introduction_tw: 聖劍士之一，擁有一擊衝破巨大城牆的猛撞力，為了保護由於人類的戰爭而失去故鄉的寶可夢而與人類作戰

name: Virizion
introduction_tw: 聖劍士之一，以敏捷的身手像旋風一般將敵人玩弄於股掌之中，會用鋒利的角毫不留情地切斬對手

name: Tornadus - Incarnate Forme
introduction_tw: 就像天气一样阴晴不定，喜欢四处游走，在高空中极速飞行；引起暴风雨其实是它有意的的恶作剧。

name: Thundurus - Incarnate Forme
introduction_tw: 像天气一样阴晴不定，喜欢四处游走，在高空中极速飞行；引起雷暴和山火其实是它有意的的恶作剧。

name: Reshiram
introduction: Believing in the truth, Vast White Pokémon turn the world into a place of kindness. The flame from their tails can burn down the entire world.
introduction_tw: 相信真實、引導世界遍佈善良的白陽寶可夢，尾部吹出的火焰能將整個世界燃燒殆盡
introduction_en: Believing in the truth, Vast White Pokémon turn the world into a place of kindness. The flame from their tails can burn down the entire world.
introduction_kr: 진실을 믿고 온 세상을 착하게 인도하는 백양 포켓몬, 꼬리에서 내뿜는 불꽃은 온 세상을 다 태울 수 있다.

name: Zekrom
introduction: Believing in ideals, Deep Black Pokémon turn the world into a place of hope. Hiding in storms, the winding of their tails can create relentless lightning.
introduction_tw: 相信理想，引導世界遍佈希望的黑陰寶可夢，隱藏在雷雲中，尾巴旋轉起來能製造狂暴的閃電
introduction_en: Believing in ideals, Deep Black Pokémon turn the world into a place of hope. Hiding in storms, the winding of their tails can create relentless lightning.
introduction_kr: 이상을 쫓아 새로운 희망의 세계로 인도하려는 흑음포켓몬, 뇌운 속에 숨어있으며 꼬리가 돌면 광폭한 번개를 만들 수 있다.

name: Landorus - Incarnate Forme
introduction_tw: 很少出现在人们面前，只有当人们共同祈愿时会现身给予人们丰收的希望，或者在雷电云和龙卷云大肆作乱之时才会现身并制止它们过度的恶作剧。在人们心中它是正义的丰收之神。

name: Kyurem
introduction: The Ice Legendary Pokémon is a hero waiting to fill its lost body with ideals and the truth.
introduction_tw: 等待著用真實與理想填補自己失去的身體的英雄，是冰之傳說的寶可夢。
introduction_en: The Ice Legendary Pokémon is a hero waiting to fill its lost body with ideals and the truth.

name: Keldeo
introduction: Through a hard battle, the inheritor of the Swords of Justice is chosen. A deep-sleeping power in the body will wrap the horn of its forehead, shaping a sword that can tear everything.
introduction_tw: 聖劍士的傳承者，通過艱苦的戰鬥而覺悟，沉睡在身體深處的力量包裹住了它額頭上的角，形成了能撕裂一切的劍。
introduction_en: Through a hard battle, the inheritor of the Swords of Justice is chosen. A deep-sleeping power in the body will wrap the horn of its forehead, shaping a sword that can tear everything.

name: Meloetta - Aria
introduction_tw: 旋律寶可夢，可以用特殊的發聲法唱出美妙的音律，這種音律能夠自由自在地操縱聽者的情感，使聽者的情感隨之變化

name: Meloetta - Pirouette
introduction_tw: 旋律寶可夢，在美洛耶塔唱出古老之歌時，會變身成舞者的形態並翩翩起舞

name: Genesect
introduction_tw: 蓋諾賽克特體型為巨型蟲類，紫色的鎧甲包裹著它的身體。背上裝有威力驚人的巨炮，可以在上面插上不同屬性的卡帶。蓋諾賽克特還可以變成圓盤狀以方便飛行

name: Chespin
introduction: Such a thick shell of wood covers its head and back that even a direct hit from a truck wouldn't faze it.
introduction_tw: 頭和背部用堅硬的木殼覆蓋著，所以即使被卡車撞到也安然無恙。
introduction_en: Such a thick shell of wood covers its head and back that even a direct hit from a truck wouldn't faze it.
introduction_vn: Đầu và lưng được bọc một lớp vỏ gỗ cứng, ngay cả khi bị xe tải đâm vào vẫn bình yên vô sự
introduction_kr: 머리와 등이 단단한 껍데기로 덮여 있기 때문에 트럭이 부딪혀와도 아무렇지 않다.

name: Quilladin
introduction: They strengthen their lower bodies by running into one another. They are very kind and won't start fights.
introduction_tw: 夥伴之間互相碰撞身體，鍛煉腰腿。自己本身是不好鬥的溫柔性格。
introduction_en: They strengthen their lower bodies by running into one another. They are very kind and won't start fights.
introduction_vn: Đồng đội va chạm vào nhau rèn luyện cơ thể. Bản thân tính cách dịu dàng không hiếu chiến
introduction_kr: 동료끼리 몸을 서로 부딪쳐 하반신을 단련한다. 자신이 먼저 싸움을 걸지 않는 온순한 성격이다.

name: Chesnaught
introduction: When it takes a defensive posture with its fists guarding its face, it could withstand a bomb blast.
introduction_tw: 如果將雙拳合攏擋在臉前，擺出防禦的姿勢，連炸彈的直接轟炸也能承受住。
introduction_en: When it takes a defensive posture with its fists guarding its face, it could withstand a bomb blast.
introduction_vn: Nắm chặt đôi tay đặt ở phía trước và làm tư thế phòng thủ, cả ném bom cũng có thể chịu được
introduction_kr: 얼굴 앞에 두 주먹을 맞대어 방어 자세를 취하면 폭탄의 직격도 견뎌낸다.

name: Fennekin
introduction: As it walks, it munches on a twig in place of a snack. It intimidates opponents by puffing hot air out of its ears.
introduction_tw: 隨身帶著小樹枝，嘎吱嘎吱地當零食吃。從耳朵裡噴出熱氣威嚇對手。
introduction_en: As it walks, it munches on a twig in place of a snack. It intimidates opponents by puffing hot air out of its ears.
introduction_vn: Mang theo cành cây nhỏ, ăn nó như món ăn nhẹ. Khí nóng phát ra từ tai đe dọa đối thủ.
introduction_kr: 작은 나뭇가지를 들고 다니며 간식 대신 아작아작 먹는다. 귀에서 열기를 뿜어내어 상대를 위협한다.
location_vn: Vũ Đạo Hỏa Diễm & Hỗ trợ dạng tấn công

name: Braixen
introduction: When the twig is plucked from its tail, friction sets the twig alight. The flame is used to send signals to its allies.
introduction_tw: 將樹枝從尾巴上拔出時，會因為摩擦而起火。揮動樹枝的火焰向夥伴傳遞信號。
introduction_en: When the twig is plucked from its tail, friction sets the twig alight. The flame is used to send signals to its allies.
introduction_vn: Khi kéo cành cây ra khỏi đuôi, sẽ bị bắt lửa do ma sát. Vẫy ngọn lửa cành cây để truyền tín hiệu cho đồng đội.
introduction_kr: 나뭇가지를 꼬리에서 뽑을 때 마찰로 불이 붙는다. 나뭇가지의 불꽃을 흔들어 동료에게 신호를 보낸다.
location_vn: Vũ Đạo Hỏa Diễm & Hỗ trợ dạng tấn công

name: Delphox
introduction: It gazes into the flame at the tip of its branch to achieve a focused state, which allows it to see into the future.
introduction_tw: 盯著木杖前端燃燒著的火焰，集中精神的話，就能看透未來發生之事。
introduction_en: It gazes into the flame at the tip of its branch to achieve a focused state, which allows it to see into the future.
introduction_vn: Nhìn ngọn lửa đang cháy ở đầu cây gậy phía trước, nếu tập trung tinh thần sẽ thấy được chuyện xảy ra trong tương lai.
introduction_kr: 지팡이 끝의 타오르는 불꽃을 바라보며 정신을 집중하면 미래에 일어날 일을 내다볼 수 있다.
location_vn: Vũ Đạo Hỏa Diễm & Hỗ trợ dạng tấn công

name: Froakie
introduction: It protects its skin by covering its body in delicate bubbles. Beneath its happy-go-lucky air, it keeps a watchful eye on its surroundings.
introduction_tw: 用細膩的泡泡包住身體，保護皮膚。裝得無憂無慮的，實則很精明地窺視著四周。
introduction_en: It protects its skin by covering its body in delicate bubbles. Beneath its happy-go-lucky air, it keeps a watchful eye on its surroundings.
introduction_vn: Dùng bong bóng bao bọc cơ thể, bảo vệ da. Giả vờ vô tư, thực ra đang nhìn rõ mọi thứ xung quanh.
introduction_kr: "섬세한 거품으로 몸을 감싸 피부를 보호한다. 태평한 척하고 있지만, 사실은 세심하게 주위를 살피고 있다."
location_vn: Sát Thương Bạo Lực: tăng thương tốc độ

name: Frogadier
introduction: Its swiftness is unparalleled. It can scale a tower of more than 2,000 feet in a minute's time.
introduction_tw: 靈巧的身體不輸給任何人。只需１分鐘就能登上超過600米高的塔頂。
introduction_en: Its swiftness is unparalleled. It can scale a tower of more than 2,000 feet in a minute's time.
introduction_vn: Cơ thể linh hoạt không thua kém ai. Chỉ cần 1 phút có thể leo lên đỉnh tháp cao hơn 600m
introduction_kr: 민첩합은 그 누구에게도 지지 않는다. 600m를 넘는 타워의 꼭대기까지 1분이면 올라간다.
location_vn: Sát Thương Bạo Lực: tăng thương tốc độ

name: Greninja
introduction: It appears and vanishes with a ninja’s grace. It toys with its enemies using swift movements, while slicing them with throwing stars of sharpest water.
introduction_tw: 像忍者般神出鬼沒。以敏捷的動作玩弄對手，再用水之手裡劍將對方劈開。
introduction_en: It appears and vanishes with a ninja’s grace. It toys with its enemies using swift movements, while slicing them with throwing stars of sharpest water.
introduction_vn: Biến hoá tài tình như Ninja. Dùng động tác nhanh nhẹn để chiến đấu với đối thủ, sau đó dùng Water Shuriken đánh bại đối phương.
introduction_kr: 닌자처럼 신출귀몰하다. 민첩한 움직임으로 상대를 농락하면서 물의 수리검으로 벤다.
location_vn: Sát Thương Bạo Lực: tăng thương tốc độ

name: Litleo
introduction: This hot-blooded Pokémon is filled with curiosity. When it gets angry or starts fighting, its short mane gets hot.
introduction_tw: 血氣方剛且好奇心旺盛。如果生氣或是開始戰鬥，短短的鬃毛就會變熱。
introduction_en: This hot-blooded Pokémon is filled with curiosity. When it gets angry or starts fighting, its short mane gets hot.
introduction_vn: Huyết khí mạnh và khá tò mò. Nếu giận dữ hoặc bắt đầu chiến đấu, bờm ngắn sẽ trở nên nóng bỏng
introduction_kr: 혈기가 넘치고 호기심도 왕성하다. 화가 나거나 싸움이 시작되면 짧은 갈기가 뜨겁게 변한다.
location_vn: Sát Thương Tàn Cục

name: Pyroar
introduction: The temperature of its breath is over 10,000 degrees Fahrenheit, but Pyroar doesn't use it on its prey. This Pokémon prefers to eat raw meat.
introduction_tw: 會吐出攝氏6000度的氣息，但不會用於獵物。因為更喜歡吃生的肉。
introduction_en: The temperature of its breath is over 10,000 degrees Fahrenheit, but Pyroar doesn't use it on its prey. This Pokémon prefers to eat raw meat.
introduction_vn: Thở ra khí 6000 độ C, nhưng không dùng để săn mồi. Vì thích ăn thịt sống
introduction_kr: 섭씨 6000도의 숨결을 내뱉지만 사냥감에는 사용하지 않는다. 날고기를 더 좋아하기 때문이다.
location_vn: Sát Thương Tàn Cục

name: Flabébé
introduction: It's not safe without the power of a flower, but it will keep traveling around until it finds one with the color and shape it wants.
introduction_tw: 如果沒有花的力量，就會很危險。但是在找到喜愛的顏色和形狀之前，會不斷地旅行。
introduction_en: It's not safe without the power of a flower, but it will keep traveling around until it finds one with the color and shape it wants.
introduction_vn: Nếu không có sức mạnh của hoa, sẽ rất nguy hiểm. Nhưng trước khi tìm thấy màu sắc và hình dạng yêu thích, sẽ tiếp tục đi du lịch.
introduction_kr: 꽃의 힘이 없으면 위험하다. 그래도 좋아하는 색과 형태를 찾을 때까지 여행을 계속한다.
location_vn: Trị Liệu Quần Thể

name: Floette
introduction: When the flowers of a well-tended flower bed bloom, it appears and celebrates with an elegant dance.
introduction_tw: 被精心照料過的花壇裡的花一旦開放，就會現身，以華麗的舞蹈給予祝福。
introduction_en: When the flowers of a well-tended flower bed bloom, it appears and celebrates with an elegant dance.
introduction_vn: Khi hoa trong bồn hoa được chăm sóc cẩn thận và nở ra, chúng sẽ hiện thân, dùng điệu nhảy tuyệt đẹp để ban phước.
introduction_kr: "세심하게 가꾼 화단의 꽃이 피면 모습을 드러내며, 아름다운 춤으로 축복한다."
location_vn: Trị Liệu Quần Thể

name: Florges
introduction: In times long past, governors of castles would invite Florges to create flower gardens to embellish the castle domains.
introduction_tw: 過去的城堡主人們為了裝飾庭園而招待花潔夫人進入，讓其建造花園。
introduction_en: In times long past, governors of castles would invite Florges to create flower gardens to embellish the castle domains.
introduction_vn: Chủ nhân lâu đài cũ đã tiếp đãi Florges vào để trang trí vườn hoa, để họ xây dựng khu vườn
introduction_kr: 옛 성의 주인은 정원을 꾸미기 위해 플라제스를 불러 화원을 만들게 했다.
location_vn: Trị Liệu Quần Thể

name: Honedge
introduction: It wraps a blue cloth around that person's arm and drains that person's life energy completely.
introduction_tw: 用藍布卷住握劍柄之人的手臂，吸取生命直至其倒下。
introduction_en: It wraps a blue cloth around that person's arm and drains that person's life energy completely.
introduction_vn: Dùng vải xanh quấn cánh tay của người cầm kiếm, hấp thụ sinh mệnh đến khi tử vong.
introduction_kr: 검의 자루를 잡은 사람의 팔에 파란 천을 감아서 쓰러질 때까지 목숨을 빨아들인다.
location: Battle Switch & Possess Attacking and Defensive Abilities
location_en: Battle Switch & Possess Attacking and Defensive Abilities

name: Doublade
introduction: Divides into two swords after evolution, which cooperate via telepathy to coordinate attacks and slash their enemies to ribbons.
introduction_tw: 進化後分裂為2把。通過心靈感應對話，用配合攻擊砍碎敵人。
introduction_en: Divides into two swords after evolution, which cooperate via telepathy to coordinate attacks and slash their enemies to ribbons.
introduction_vn: Sau khi tiến hóa tách thành 2. Thông qua tâm linh cảm ứng để đối thoại, dùng phối hợp tấn công để đánh bại kẻ thù.
introduction_kr: 진화해 2자루로 분열되었다. 텔레파시로 서로 대화하며 연계 공격으로 적을 조각낸다.
location: Battle Switch & Possess Attacking and Defensive Abilities
location_en: Battle Switch & Possess Attacking and Defensive Abilities

name: Aegislash - Shield Forme
introduction: Generations of kings were attended by these Pokémons, which used their spectral power to manipulate and control people and Pokémons.
introduction_tw: 曾跟隨著歷代國王。用靈力控制人和寶可夢的心，使之服從。
introduction_en: Generations of kings were attended by these Pokémons, which used their spectral power to manipulate and control people and Pokémons.
introduction_vn: Từng đi theo vua của các triều đại. Dùng linh lực khống chế trái tim của người và Pokémon, khiến đối phương phục tùng.
introduction_kr: "한때 역대의 왕들을 따라다녔고, 영력으로 사람이나 포켓몬의 마음을 조종하여 복종하게 한다."
location: Battle Switch & Possess Attacking and Defensive Abilities
location_en: Battle Switch & Possess Attacking and Defensive Abilities

name: Swirlix
introduction: To entangle its opponents in battle, it extrudes white threads as sweet and sticky as cotton candy.
introduction_tw: 放出像棉花糖那樣又甜又黏的白絲纏住對手，封住其行動。
introduction_en: To entangle its opponents in battle, it extrudes white threads as sweet and sticky as cotton candy.
introduction_vn: Nhả ra sợi tơ trắng vừa ngọt vừa dính như kẹo bông gòn quấn lấy đối thủ, ngăn chặn hành động của đối phương
introduction_kr: "솜사탕 같은 달고 끈적끈적한 흰색 실을 내뿜어, 상대를 휘감아서 움직이지 못하게 한다."

name: Slurpuff
introduction: It can distinguish the faintest of scents. It puts its sensitive sense of smell to use by helping pastry chefs in their work.
introduction_tw: 擁有即便是細微氣味也能區分的敏銳嗅覺，是西點師傅的好幫手。
introduction_en: It can distinguish the faintest of scents. It puts its sensitive sense of smell to use by helping pastry chefs in their work.
introduction_vn: Với khứu giác nhạy bén có thể được phân biệt được các mùi, là trợ thủ đắc lực của Pastry
introduction_kr: "아주 약간의 냄새도 구별할 수 있는 민감한 후각을 지니고 있어, 파티시에의 훌륭한 조수 역할을 한다."

name: Clauncher
introduction: They knock down flying prey by firing compressed water from their massive claws like shooting a pistol.
introduction_tw: 像手槍一樣把壓縮過的水從大大的鉗子裡射出，擊落飛著的獵物。
introduction_en: They knock down flying prey by firing compressed water from their massive claws like shooting a pistol.
introduction_vn: Bắn nước nén ra khỏi kìm lớn như súng lục, bắn hạ con mồi đang bay.
introduction_kr: "커다란 집게발로 압축한 물을 권총처럼 쏘아, 날고 있는 사냥감을 떨어뜨린다."

name: Clawitzer
introduction: Their enormous claws launch cannonballs of water powerful enough to pierce tanker hulls.
introduction_tw: 擁有能發射水炮彈的巨大手臂，連油輪的船體也能擊穿。
introduction_en: Their enormous claws launch cannonballs of water powerful enough to pierce tanker hulls.
introduction_vn: Cánh tay khổng lồ có thể bắn đạn pháo nước, ngay cả thân tàu chở dầu cũng có thể đánh xuyên
introduction_kr: "물 포탄을 발사하는 거대한 집게발을 지녔으며, 유조선의 선체조차 뚫어버릴 수 있다."

name: Amaura
introduction: This ancient Pokémon was restored from part of its body that had been frozen in ice for over 100 million years.
introduction_tw: 從1億年前起就處於冰封狀態的身體的一部分復活而來的古代寶可夢。
introduction_en: This ancient Pokémon was restored from part of its body that had been frozen in ice for over 100 million years.
introduction_vn: Ancient Pokémon đã bị đóng băng từ 100 triệu năm trước và hồi sinh trở lại
introduction_kr: 1억 년 전부터 빙하로 뒤덮여 있던 몸의 일부에서 부활한 고대의 포켓몬이다.
location_vn: Hộ Thuẫn Quần Thể

name: Aurorus
introduction: The diamond-shaped crystals on its body expel air as cold as -240 degrees Fahrenheit, surrounding its enemies and encasing them in ice.
introduction_tw: 從身上的菱形結晶裡放出零下150度的冷氣，把敵人包住並冰封起來。
introduction_en: The diamond-shaped crystals on its body expel air as cold as -240 degrees Fahrenheit, surrounding its enemies and encasing them in ice.
introduction_vn: Từ kết tinh trên cơ thể phát ra khí lạnh âm 150 độ, bao bọc và đóng băng kẻ thù.
introduction_kr: "영하 150도의 냉기를 마름모꼴의 결정에서 내뿜어, 적을 감싸 얼어붙게 만든다."
location_vn: Hộ Thuẫn Quần Thể

name: Hawlucha
introduction: Although its body is small, its proficient fighting skills enable it to keep up with big bruisers like Machamp and Hariyama.
introduction_tw: 體型雖小，卻是個技術高手。與怪力和鐵掌力士等大型寶可夢戰鬥起來都難分伯仲。
introduction_en: Although its body is small, its proficient fighting skills enable it to keep up with big bruisers like Machamp and Hariyama.
introduction_vn: Thân hình tuy nhỏ nhưng là cao thủ kỹ thuật. Chiến đấu với Superpower Pokémon và Hariyama cũng khó phân cao thấp.
introduction_kr: 체격은 작지만 테크니션이다. 괴력몬이나 하리뭉 등의 커다란 포켓몬과 막상막하로 싸울 수 있다.
location: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_en: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_vn: Sát Thương Vận Lực: tiêu diệt toàn MAP

name: Goomy
introduction: The weakest Dragon-type Pokémon, it lives in damp, shady places, so its body doesn't dry out.
introduction_tw: 是最弱小的龍屬性寶可夢。為了防止滑膩膩的身體變幹，而呆在濕噠噠的背陰處生活。
introduction_en: The weakest Dragon-type Pokémon, it lives in damp, shady places, so its body doesn't dry out.
introduction_vn: Đây là Pokémon thuộc tính rồng yếu nhất. Sống ở nơi ẩm ướt để cơ thể không bị khô.
introduction_kr: 가장 약한 드래곤 타입 포켓몬이다. 미끌미끌한 몸이 마르지 않도록 축축한 그늘에서 산다.
location: Critical hit and SP. DEF Shield
location_en: Critical hit and SP. DEF Shield

name: Sliggoo
introduction: It drives away opponents by excreting a sticky liquid that can dissolve anything. Its eyes devolved, so it can't see anything.
introduction_tw: 分泌出可以溶解任何物體的粘液擊退敵人。眼珠退化，看不見東西。
introduction_en: It drives away opponents by excreting a sticky liquid that can dissolve anything. Its eyes devolved, so it can't see anything.
introduction_vn: Tiết ra chất nhầy hòa tan bất kỳ vật thể và đánh bại kẻ thù. Nhãn cầu thoái hóa, không thể nhìn thấy gì.
introduction_kr: 무엇이든 녹여버리는 점액을 분비해 적을 격퇴한다. 눈은 퇴화하여 보이지 않는다.
location: Critical hit and SP. DEF Shield
location_en: Critical hit and SP. DEF Shield

name: Goodra
introduction: This very friendly Dragon-type Pokémon will hug its beloved Trainer, leaving that Trainer covered in sticky slime.
introduction_tw: 和人很親近的龍屬性寶可夢。抱著非常喜愛的訓練家，用粘液把對方弄得黏糊糊的。
introduction_en: This very friendly Dragon-type Pokémon will hug its beloved Trainer, leaving that Trainer covered in sticky slime.
introduction_vn: Pokémon thuộc tính rồng gần gũi với con người. Là một nhà huấn luyện được yêu thích, dùng chất nhầy để khiến đối phương bị dính lại  .
introduction_kr: 사람을 잘 따르는 드래곤 타입 포켓몬이다. 좋아하는 트레이너에게 달려들어 미끈미끈한 점액투성이로 만들어 버린다.
location: Critical hit and SP. DEF Shield
location_en: Critical hit and SP. DEF Shield

name: Phantump
introduction: These Pokémon are created when spirits possess rotten tree stumps. They prefer to live in abandoned forests.
introduction_tw: 魂魄寄生在腐爛的樹樁上，變成了寶可夢。居住在人類不會接近的森林。
introduction_en: These Pokémon are created when spirits possess rotten tree stumps. They prefer to live in abandoned forests.
introduction_vn: Hồn phách ký sinh trên gốc cây mục nát, trở thành Pokémon. Sống trong một khu rừng nơi con người không tiếp cận.
introduction_kr: 썩은 그루터기에 혼이 깃들어 포켓몬이 되었다. 사람이 가까이 오지 않는 숲에 산다.
location_vn: Trầm Mặc Hàng Sau

name: Trevenant
introduction: It can control trees at will. It will trap people who harm the forest, so they can never leave.
introduction_tw: 可以自由地操縱其他的樹木。會讓毀壞森林的人類到死都沒法走出森林。
introduction_en: It can control trees at will. It will trap people who harm the forest, so they can never leave.
introduction_vn: Có thể tự do thao túng những cây khác. Khiến những người phá rừng đến chết cũng không thể ra khỏi khu rừng.
introduction_kr: 다른 나무들을 자유자재로 조종한다. 숲을 파괴하는 인간은 죽을 때까지 숲에서 벗어나지 못하게 만든다.
location_vn: Trầm Mặc Hàng Sau

name: Noibat
introduction: No wavelength of sound is beyond Noibat's ability to produce. The ultrasonic waves it generates can overcome much larger Pokémon.
introduction_tw: 可以控制所有頻率的音波。就算是體型巨大的寶可夢，也對它的超音波束手無策。
introduction_en: No wavelength of sound is beyond Noibat's ability to produce. The ultrasonic waves it generates can overcome much larger Pokémon.
introduction_kr: 거의 모든 주파수의 음파를 조종할 수 있다. 거대한 몸집의 포켓몬도 녀석의 초음파는 견디지 못한다.

name: Noivern
introduction: Flying through the darkness, it weakens enemies with ultrasonic waves that could crush stone. Its fangs finish the fight.
introduction_tw: 在黑暗中一邊飛行一邊發出能粉碎岩石的超音波痛擊敵人，然後用利齒給予致命的一擊。
introduction_en: Flying through the darkness, it weakens enemies with ultrasonic waves that could crush stone. Its fangs finish the fight.
introduction_kr: 어둠 속을 날아다니며 바위도 부수는 초음파로 타격을 입힌 뒤 예리한 이빨로 숨통을 끊는다.

name: Xerneas
introduction_tw: 司掌生命的傳說寶可夢，以樹木的樣子睡了1000年後復活，據說，當頭上的角閃著七色光時，會分享永恆的生命。

name: Yveltal
introduction_tw: 司掌死亡的傳說寶可夢，一度以破壞之繭形態沉睡在森林深處，翅膀和尾羽展開閃著紅色光芒時，就會吸取生物的生命，並將其石化

name: Diancie
introduction: A Jewel Pokémon. A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.
introduction_tw: 幻之寶可夢，小碎鑽的突變體，全身閃耀著粉色光芒，被認為是世間最美麗的。
introduction_en: A Jewel Pokémon. A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.
introduction_vn: Magic Pokémon, thể đột biến của viên kim ương vỡ nhỏ, với ánh sáng màu hồng rực rỡ toàn thân, được coi là đẹp nhất thế gian
introduction_kr: "환상의 포켓몬으로, 멜리시의 돌연변이다. 분홍빛으로 빛나는 몸은 세상에서 가장 아름답다고 여겨진다."
location_vn: Công Chúa Kim Cương & Hỗ Trợ Hoàn Hảo

name: Mega Diancie
introduction: A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.
introduction_tw: 小碎鑽的突變體。閃著粉紅色光輝的身體被贊為全世界最美。
introduction_en: A sudden transformation of Carbink, its pink, glimmering body is said to be the loveliest sight in the whole world.
introduction_vn: Thể đột biến của viên kim ương vỡ nhỏ. Cơ thể với màu hồng rực rỡ được ca ngợi là đẹp nhất thế giới.
introduction_kr: "멜리시의 돌연변이, 분홍빛으로 빛나는 몸은 세상에서 가장 아름답다고 여겨진다."

name: Hoopa Confined
introduction: Mischief Pokémon, characterized by two horns and a golden ring, is a troublemaker that likes using its space-warping ring to send everything to faraway places.
introduction_tw: 頑童寶可夢，以兩根角和身上套著的金色圓環為特徵，是個喜歡用能扭曲空間的圓環把所有東西都擊飛到遠處的麻煩製造者
introduction_en: Mischief Pokémon, characterized by two horns and a golden ring, is a troublemaker that likes using its space-warping ring to send everything to faraway places.
introduction_kr: 개구쟁이 포켓몬은 두 개의 뿔과 몸에 걸친 금색 고리를 특징으로, 공간을 뒤틀 수 있는 둥근 고리로 모든 것을 멀리 날려버리는 것을 좋아하는 귀찮은 제조자이다.
location: Small Djinn of Golden Ring & Space Switcher
location_tw: 光輪的小魔神&異度轉移
location_en: Small Djinn of Golden Ring & Space Switcher

name: Hoopa Unbound
introduction: Djinn Pokémon, confined Hoopa's true posture. It has an even bigger body than the confined forme, characterized by six arms and more rings. It is said that it can snatch everything by using its space-warping ring.
introduction_tw: 魔神寶可夢，被封印了的胡帕的真正姿態。比被封印形態更加巨大的身體、增加的圓環和6只手臂是它的特徵。據說會使用可以扭曲空間的圓環搶奪一切
introduction_en: Djinn Pokémon, confined Hoopa's true posture. It has an even bigger body than the confined forme, characterized by six arms and more rings. It is said that it can snatch everything by using its space-warping ring.
introduction_kr: 마신포켓몬,봉인된 후파의 참모습봉인된 형태보다 더 큰 몸집, 늘어난 둥근 고리, 6개의 팔뚝이 특징이다.공간을 뒤틀어놓을 수 있는 둥근 고리를 사용해서 모든 걸 뺏는다고 하더라고요.
location: Super Djinn of Golden Ring & Space Switcher
location_tw: 光輪的超魔神&異度轉移
location_en: Super Djinn of Golden Ring & Space Switcher

name: Rowlet
introduction: Rowlet, Grass Quill Pokémon, Grass/Flying type. Can store energy from photosynthesis during the day. It swoops down without making a sound and unleashes a powerful kick without being noticed.
introduction_tw: 木木梟，草羽寶可夢，草跟飛行屬性。白天會利用光合作用囤積力量。會無聲無息的飛行，突然沖向敵人，趁對方不注意的時候，使出猛烈的踢擊。
introduction_en: Rowlet, Grass Quill Pokémon, Grass/Flying type. Can store energy from photosynthesis during the day. It swoops down without making a sound and unleashes a powerful kick without being noticed.
introduction_kr: "나몰빼미, 풀깃 포켓몬, 풀과 비행 타입이다. 낮에는 광합성으로 힘을 비축한다. 전혀 소리를 내지 않고 비행하며, 적에게 갑자기 돌진한다. 상대가 눈치채기 전에 강렬한 발차기를 퍼붓는다."
location: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_en: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_vn: Sát Thương Vận Lực: tiêu diệt toàn MAP

name: Dartrix
introduction: Dartrix, Blade Quill Pokémon, Grass/Flying type. It throws its very sharp feathers like darts at enemies. Dartrix pays much attention to its appearance and is always preening.
introduction_tw: 投羽梟，刃羽寶可夢，草跟飛行屬性。牠會將被稱為刃羽的銳利羽毛，丟向敵人和獵物，很重視外表，總是在整理羽毛。
introduction_en: Dartrix, Blade Quill Pokémon, Grass/Flying type. It throws its very sharp feathers like darts at enemies. Dartrix pays much attention to its appearance and is always preening.
introduction_kr: "빼미스로우, 칼날깃 포켓몬, 풀과 비행 타입이다. 칼날깃이라고 불리는 날카로운 날개를 적이나 사냥감에게 날린다. 외모를 중시하며, 항상 날개의 손질을 한다."
location: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_en: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_vn: Sát Thương Vận Lực: tiêu diệt toàn MAP

name: Decidueye
introduction: Decidueye, Arrow Quill Pokémon, Grass/Ghost type. Decidueye can fire arrow quills with such precision that it can hit a pebble over a hundred yards away.
introduction_tw: 狙射樹梟，箭羽寶可夢，草跟幽靈屬性。牠會把藏在翅膀裡的箭羽像弓箭一樣射出，準確度高連100公尺外的小石頭都能被射穿。
introduction_en: Decidueye, Arrow Quill Pokémon, Grass/Ghost type. Decidueye can fire arrow quills with such precision that it can hit a pebble over a hundred yards away.
introduction_kr: "모크나이퍼, 화살깃 포켓몬, 풀과 고스트 타입이다. 날개에 숨겨진 살깃을 화살처럼 날린다. 100m 밖의 작은 돌도 관통하는 정확도를 선보인다."
location: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_en: Charging damage: Tap and kill all enemies
location_vn: Sát Thương Vận Lực: tiêu diệt toàn MAP

name: Mareanie
introduction: Mareanie, Brutal Star Pokémon, Poison/Water type. Equipped with poisonous head spikes, it can trap its prey with 10 legs by turning upside down.
introduction_tw: 好壞星，非星寶可夢，是毒跟水屬性。頭上有有毒的尖刺，會用十隻觸手跳起來，翻轉身體後再攻擊敵人。
introduction_en: Mareanie, Brutal Star Pokémon, Poison/Water type. Equipped with poisonous head spikes, it can trap its prey with 10 legs by turning upside down.
introduction_kr: 시마사리,비성포켓몬은 독과 물의 타입이다.머리에 독이 있는 날카로운 가시가 있으면 열 개로 튕겨 몸을 뒤척이며 적을 공격한다.

name: Toxapex
introduction: It uses 12 legs to crawl on the bottom of the sea. Toxapex leaves a trail of Corsola bits scattered on its way.
introduction_tw: 用１２只腳在海底爬行。在超壞星爬過的地方會散落太陽珊瑚的碎屑。
introduction_en: It uses 12 legs to crawl on the bottom of the sea. Toxapex leaves a trail of Corsola bits scattered on its way.
introduction_kr: 12 발로 해저를 기어가다.더시마사리가 기어가는 곳에서는 태양산호의 부스러기가 흩어진다.

name: Bounsweet
introduction: Bounsweet, Fruit Pokémon, Grass type. Lured by a delicious scent that Bounsweet emits from its body, many flying Pokémon mistake it for a berry.
introduction_tw: 甜竹竹，水果寶可夢，草屬性。體內會散發出聞起來很美味的香氣，被這個香味引誘，有很多的鳥寶可夢都會以為是真的水果。
introduction_en: Bounsweet, Fruit Pokémon, Grass type. Lured by a delicious scent that Bounsweet emits from its body, many flying Pokémon mistake it for a berry.
introduction_kr: 달콤아,과일 포켓몬, 풀의 타입.맛있는 냄새가 나는 몸에 유혹되어 진짜 과일인 줄 아는 새들이 많다.

name: Steenee
introduction: Steenee, Fruit Pokémon, Grass type. Steenee is protected by highly developed hard sepals that make its Double Slap attack very powerful.
introduction_tw: 甜舞妮，水果寶可夢，是草屬性。為了保護身體有著堅硬的殼蓋，所以她使出的連環巴掌具有相當大的威力。
introduction_en: Steenee, Fruit Pokémon, Grass type. Steenee is protected by highly developed hard sepals that make its Double Slap attack very powerful.
introduction_kr: 달무리나과일 포켓몬, 풀의 타입.몸을 보호하기 위해 딱딱한 껍데기를 갖고 있기 때문에 그의 손끝 연쇄는 상당한 위력을 발휘한다.

name: Ice Queen
introduction: Tsareena, Fruit Pokémon, Grass type. Tsareena has very strong legs, making its kicking attacks very powerful. It steps on defeated opponents to signalize its victories. It's said that when one touches the crown-like part of Tsareena's head, its power will perish.
introduction_tw: 甜冷美後，水果寶可夢，草屬性。擅長使用腳踢招式，會踩著落敗的對手誇耀勝利。據說甜冷美後頭頂像王冠一樣的部位一旦被觸碰，力量便會消失。
introduction_en: Tsareena, Fruit Pokémon, Grass type. Tsareena has very strong legs, making its kicking attacks very powerful. It steps on defeated opponents to signalize its victories. It's said that when one touches the crown-like part of Tsareena's head, its power will perish.
introduction_kr: 달코퀸,과일 포켓몬,풀의 타입.발차기를 잘하면 지는 상대를 밟아 승리를 자랑한다.달코퀸 왕관 같은 부위가 닿으면 힘이 사라진다고 한다.

name: Solgaleo
introduction: It is said to live in another world. The intense light it radiates from the surface of its body can make the darkest of nights light up like midday.
introduction_tw: 據說是棲息在其他世界的。全身放出猛烈的光芒，即使是暗夜也會照得如同白晝。
introduction_en: It is said to live in another world. The intense light it radiates from the surface of its body can make the darkest of nights light up like midday.
introduction_vn: Tương truyền sống ở các thế giới khác. Toàn thân phát ra ánh sáng mãnh liệt, dù là ban đêm cũng sẽ tỏa sáng như ban ngày.
introduction_kr: 다른 세계에 산다고 전해진다. 온몸에서 격렬한 빛을 내뿜어 깜깜한 밤도 한낮처럼 비춘다.
location: The Beast That Devours the Sun
location_en: The Beast That Devours the Sun
location_vn: Thú Nuốt Chửng Mặt Trời

name: Poipole
introduction: Poison Pin Pokémon, an Ultra Beast that lives in a different world. It cackles wildly as it sprays its opponents with poison from the needles on its head.
introduction_tw: 毒針寶可夢，棲息在異世界的究極異獸。會從頭部的毒針朝對手噴出毒液，咯咯咯大笑。
introduction_en: Poison Pin Pokémon, an Ultra Beast that lives in a different world. It cackles wildly as it sprays its opponents with poison from the needles on its head.
introduction_kr: 독침 포켓몬,이세계에 서식하는 궁극의 이수.머리의 독침에서 상대를 향해 독액을 내뿜으며 깔깔 웃는다.

name: Naganadel
introduction: Poison Pin Pokémon, one of the Ultra Beasts. It shoots a very sticky and luminous venom from its needles.
introduction_tw: 毒針寶可夢，究極異獸中的一種。會從毒針發射出黏性很大又發光的毒液。
introduction_en: Poison Pin Pokémon, one of the Ultra Beasts. It shoots a very sticky and luminous venom from its needles.
introduction_kr: 독침 포켓몬,극이수 중의 한 종을 구명하다.독침에서 점성이 크고 발광하는 독액이 발사된다.

introduction_tw: 從手腳的肉球放電。當捷拉奧拉賓士而過時，周圍將充斥著電閃雷鳴
身體是融化成液狀的鋼鐵。它能夠將土壤中的鐵或其它金屬溶解後吸收進體內。
因為擁有產出鐵的力量而受到崇拜。壽命快到盡頭的時候，身體就會生銹解體。到最後細小的碎片會復活為美錄坦。
小智最初的夥伴，拒絕進化，也不願意呆在精靈球中。時而毀天滅地，時而一擊即敗，榮獲多次奧斯卡影帝稱號，人生如戲，全靠演技

name: Ditto - Purple
introduction: Purple Ditto, the Transform Pokémon. It is able to rearrange the cells of its body and assume any form. Its only attack is Transform.
introduction_tw: 紫色百變怪，變身寶可夢。可以自由自在的重組身體的細胞，有變身能力的寶可夢。絕招只有一個，就是變身。
introduction_en: Purple Ditto, the Transform Pokémon. It is able to rearrange the cells of its body and assume any form. Its only attack is Transform.
introduction_vn: Purple Ditto, Transform Pokémon. Có thể tự sắp xếp lại tế bào của cơ thể, Pokémon có khả năng biến thân. Chỉ có 1 tuyệt chiêu là biến thân
introduction_kr: "보라색 메타몽, 변신 포켓몬, 몸의 세포를 재구성해 변신하는 능력이 있다. 뛰어난 기술은 단 하나, 변신뿐이다."
location_vn: Nguyên Liệu Tăng Sao

introduction_en: Orange Ditto, the Transform Pokémon. It is able to rearrange the cells of its body and assume any form. Its only attack is Transform.
introduction_vn: Orange Ditto, Transform Pokémon. Có thể tự sắp xếp lại tế bào của cơ thể, Pokémon có khả năng biến thân. Chỉ có 1 tuyệt chiêu là biến thân

location_vn: Nguyên Liệu Tăng Sao Thường
